@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="content-page">
    <div class="content-page-inner">

            <div class="content-header">
                <div class="content-eyebrow">Legal</div>
                <h1 class="content-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="content-meta">Last updated: June 1, 2026</p>
            </div>

                <div class="content-body">

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                        <p>When you use LandIt, we collect information you provide directly to us, including:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Account information such as your name, email address, and password</li>
                            <li>Resume files and career-related content you upload</li>
                            <li>Job titles, company names, and job descriptions you submit for analysis</li>
                            <li>Booking details and session notes related to mock interviews</li>
                            <li>Payment information processed securely through our payment provider</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Provide, maintain, and improve the LandIt platform</li>
                            <li>Process bookings and facilitate mock interview sessions</li>
                            <li>Generate ATS resume analysis and AI-powered interview questions</li>
                            <li>Send you service-related communications</li>
                            <li>Respond to your comments and questions</li>
                            <li>Monitor and analyse usage patterns to improve user experience</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
                        <p>
                            We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.
                            We may share your information only in the following circumstances:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>With recruiters you book sessions with, limited to what is necessary for the session</li>
                            <li>With service providers who assist in operating our platform (e.g. payment processors)</li>
                            <li>When required by law or to protect the rights and safety of our users</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
                        <p>
                            We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal
                            information against unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
                            However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>5. Resume & File Storage</h2>
                        <p>
                            Resume files you upload are stored securely and used solely for the purpose of ATS
                            analysis and resume generation. We do not share your resume with third parties
                            without your explicit consent. You may delete your uploaded resumes at any time
                            from your account settings.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
                        <p>You have the right to:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
                            <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
                            <li>Request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
                            <li>Withdraw consent where processing is based on consent</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:farahhh.adel@gmail.com">admin@@landit</a>.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
                        <p>
                            LandIt uses cookies to maintain your session, remember your theme preference
                            (dark/light mode), and improve your experience. You can control cookie settings
                            through your browser, though disabling cookies may affect platform functionality.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                        <p>
                            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of
                            significant changes by posting the new policy on this page with an updated date.
                            Continued use of LandIt after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
                        <p>
                            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
                    <a href="mailto:farahhh.adel@gmail.com">admin@@landit</a> or through our
                            <a href="/Home/Contact">contact page</a>.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        @section Head {
            <style>
                .content-page {
                    padding: 5rem 2.5rem;
                }

                .content-page-inner {
                    max-width: 720px;
                    margin: 0 auto;
                }

                .content-header {
                    margin-bottom: 3rem;
                    padding-bottom: 2rem;
                    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
                }

                .content-eyebrow {
                    font-size: 0.7rem;
                    font-weight: 500;
                    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
                    color: var(--blue);
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
                }

                .content-title {
                    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
                    font-size: 2rem;
                    font-weight: 700;
                    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
                    color: var(--text);
                    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
                }

                .content-meta {
                    font-size: 0.85rem;
                    color: var(--muted);
                }

                .content-body {
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    gap: 2rem;
                }

                .content-section h2 {
                    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
                    font-size: 1rem;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    color: var(--text);
                    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
                }

                .content-section p {
                    font-size: 0.9rem;
                    color: var(--muted2);
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
                }

                .content-section ul {
                    padding-left: 1.25rem;
                    display: flex;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    gap: 0.4rem;
                }

                    .content-section ul li {
                        font-size: 0.9rem;
                        color: var(--muted2);
                        line-height: 1.7;
                    }

                .content-section a {
                    color: var(--blue);
                    text-decoration: underline;
                    text-underline-offset: 3px;
                }
            </style>
        }
